ing to enhance their viewing experience, sportsbooks offer exciting ways to engage with the games, providing opportunities to place bets and predict outcomes.\", \"from\": 500, \"to\": 686, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can engage with and place bets with a sportsbook likehttps://sportsbook.fanduel.com/.\", \"from\": 687, \"to\": 776, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Venues and AtmosphereThe choice of venues for the soccer tournament ensures a mix of historic stadiums and modern arenas, each providing a unique atmosphere.\", \"from\": 778, \"to\": 935, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Notable venues include:  \\u25cf Parc des Princes in Paris: A historic stadium with a rich legacy, it will host several key matches, including some knockout rounds.\", \"from\": 936, \"to\": 1094, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 963, \"end\": 979, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Parc_des_Princes\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Parc des Princes\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Parc_des_Princes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Parc_des_Princes\"}, {\"begin\": 983, \"end\": 988, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 7.517278594679443e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u25cf Stade de Marseille: Known for its passionate fans, this venue will undoubtedly provide a vibrant backdrop for the matches it hosts.\", \"from\": 1096, \"to\": 1229, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u25cf Stade de Lyon: Located in D\\u00e9cines-Charpieu, this stadium is known for its excellent facilities and will be a crucial venue in the tournament.\", \"from\": 1231, \"to\": 1374, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"These venues are expected to be filled with enthusiastic fans, creating an electric atmosphere that will inspire the players an